OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly morning showers will
OL,6,Fquickly clear to leave a sunny day,
OL,7,Fthough the sunshine turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly hazy through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. The risk of some mist and
OL,10,Ffog along the coast at times. Feeling
OL,11,Fwarm but also rather breezy at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA mostly dry evening and
OL,14,Fnight with plenty of clear spells.
OL,15,FSome low cloud developing over the
OL,16,Fhills during the early hours. Staying
OL,17,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
