OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA fresher feeling day with
OL,6,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells. The
OL,7,Frisk of a few showers developing,
OL,8,Fmainly in the north. Breezy along the
OL,9,Fcoast and over the hills.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fbright start to Saturday, but heavy
OL,13,Frain moving in later on in the day.
OL,14,FSunshine and showers for Sunday and
OL,15,Fthen potentially wetter and winder on
OL,16,FMonday. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
